Banks - 
<bibRefCitation author="Krishna, K" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History" pageId="5" pageNumber="36" pagination="303 - 408" title="Generic revision and phylogenetic study of the family Kalotermitidae (Isoptera)." volume="122" year="1961">Krishna 1961</bibRefCitation>
